        "title": "第５回教育の為のＴＯＣシンポジウム",
        "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 'ＭＳ 明朝',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: Century; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 'ＭＳ 明朝'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Century; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">第５回教育の為のＴＯＣシンポジウムに参加しました。<br /><br />学んだ事を箇条書きに記載致します。<br /><br /></span></p><pclass=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span style=\"font-family: 'ＭＳ 明朝',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: Century; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 'ＭＳ 明朝'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Century; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">年夏に、上陸し、教育の為のＴＯＣがスタートした。</span></p><pclass=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 'ＭＳ 明朝',serif; mso-ascii-font-family: Century; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 'ＭＳ 明朝'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Century; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin;\">ＴＯＣ＝</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #252525; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">theory of constraints</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'ＭＳ 明朝', serif; color: #252525; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">＝制約理論</span></p><pclass=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'ＭＳ 明朝', serif; color: #252525; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">成果＝知識（何を頭に入れるのか？）＋訓練（どうやって頭を使うのか？）</span></p><pclass=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'ＭＳ 明朝', serif; color: #252525; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">人間関係の重要さを見くびってはならない。</span></p><pclass=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'ＭＳ 明朝', serif; color: #252525; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">ゴールドラット博士は、シンブルになるある法則があるはずと考えている。</span></p><pclass=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'ＭＳ 明朝', serif; color: #252525; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">人のせいにしても問題は解決はしない。</span></p><pclass=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'ＭＳ 明朝', serif; color: #252525; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><br />ＴＯＣの</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #252525; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'ＭＳ 明朝', serif; color: #252525; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">つの信念。（科学者のように考える。）</span></p><pclass=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'ＭＳ 明朝', serif; color: #252525; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">１．そもそもシンプルである。</span></p><pclass=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'ＭＳ 明朝', serif; color: #252525; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">２．人は、元々善良である。</span></p><pclass=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'ＭＳ 明朝', serif; color: #252525; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">３．ウイン・ウィンは、常に可能である。</span></p><pclass=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'ＭＳ 明朝', serif; color: #252525; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">４．わかっているとは、決して言わない。<br /><br /></span></p><pclass=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'ＭＳ 明朝', serif; color: #252525; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">月曜日が楽しみな会社・学校にしょう。</span></p><pclass=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'ＭＳ 明朝', serif; color: #252525; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">教育の中では、答えを教えるより、考えさせる事が大切。</span></p><pclass=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'ＭＳ 明朝', serif; color: #252525; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">自分で考え、自分で行動すれば、忘れにくく、覚えている。</span></p><pclass=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p><pclass=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'ＭＳ 明朝', serif; color: #252525; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">考える訓練をし、考える力をつける事が大切。</span></p>",
